```html
<template>
  <div class="exciting-features">
    <h2 class="heading">New Exciting Features Are Being Developed!</h2>
    <p class="sub-text">Stay tuned for the latest updates and enhancements to make your experience even better.</p>

    <div class="feature-list">
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon red"></div>
        <p class="feature-text">A Modern Cloud Based POS system</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon green"></div>
        <p class="feature-text">Staff productivity and rate of client engagement</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon yellow"></div>
        <p class="feature-text">Inventory Management, Sales and wastage reports</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</template>

<style scoped>
  .exciting-features {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .heading {
    color: #e74c3c;
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .sub-text {
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .feature-list {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
  }

  .feature-item {
    flex-shrink: 1;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin: 0 10px;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .red {
    background-color: #e74c3c;
  }

  .green {
    background-color: #4caf50;
  }

  .yellow {
    background-color: #f39c12;
  }

  .feature-text {
    color: #333;
  }
</style>
```

